title.rendered: Outright Bungalow For Sale In Saket | Exclusive Mandate

content.rendered:
The basics of buying any Real Estate are focused on Location Location and Location.

This stunning contemporary Bungalow Location is nestled in Saket which is renowned for upscale shopping complexes & commercial hubs, and hospitals and is known for its proximity to NCR. The South Delhi prospective Bungalow plot is on a sprawling 375yds that adjoins a huge decorated ornamental park, overlooks an infinite green belt & flaunts serene views of the iconic monument of Qutub Minar. It has excellent connectivity from Saket metro station and is in close proximity to PVR Anupam, Saket City Walk, DLF Mall, Sheraton Hotel, Max Hospital, and Qutub Golf course.
♕375sqyds
♕Outright Bungalow sale
♕Prominent Location
♕Crystal Clear Title
♕Infinite Green Views
♕Adjoins Huge Decorated Park
♕Three Side Corner
♕Freehold Property
♕Exclusive Mandate
♕All Cheque Payment
Lalit Kaushik
